  "root_text": {
    "iti24:0.1": "Itivuttaka 24 ",
    "iti24:0.2": "Ekakanipāta ",
    "iti24:0.3": "Tatiyavagga ",
    "iti24:0.4": "Aṭṭhipuñjasutta ",
    "iti24:1.1": "Vuttañhetaṁ bhagavatā vuttamarahatāti me sutaṁ: ",
    "iti24:2.1": "“Ekapuggalassa, bhikkhave, kappaṁ sandhāvato saṁsarato siyā evaṁ mahā aṭṭhikaṅkalo aṭṭhipuñjo aṭṭhirāsi yathāyaṁ vepullo pabbato, sace saṁhārako assa, sambhatañca na vinasseyyā”ti. ",
    "iti24:2.2": "Etamatthaṁ bhagavā avoca. ",
    "iti24:2.3": "Tatthetaṁ iti vuccati: ",
    "iti24:3.1": "“Ekassekena kappena, ",
    "iti24:3.2": "puggalassaṭṭhisañcayo; ",
    "iti24:3.3": "Siyā pabbatasamo rāsi, ",
    "iti24:3.4": "iti vuttaṁ mahesinā. ",
    "iti24:4.1": "So kho panāyaṁ akkhāto, ",
    "iti24:4.2": "vepullo pabbato mahā; ",
    "iti24:4.3": "Uttaro gijjhakūṭassa, ",
    "iti24:4.4": "magadhānaṁ giribbaje. ",
    "iti24:5.1": "Yato ca ariyasaccāni, ",
    "iti24:5.2": "sammappaññāya passati; ",
    "iti24:5.3": "Dukkhaṁ dukkhasamuppādaṁ, ",
    "iti24:5.4": "dukkhassa ca atikkamaṁ; ",
    "iti24:5.5": "Ariyañcaṭṭhaṅgikaṁ maggaṁ, ",
    "iti24:5.6": "dukkhūpasamagāminaṁ. ",
    "iti24:6.1": "Sa sattakkhattuṁ paramaṁ, ",
    "iti24:6.2": "sandhāvitvāna puggalo; ",
    "iti24:6.3": "Dukkhassantakaro hoti, ",
    "iti24:6.4": "sabbasaṁyojanakkhayā”ti. ",
    "iti24:7.1": "Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. ",
    "iti24:7.2": "Catutthaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "iti24:0.1": "So It Was Said 24 ",
    "iti24:0.2": "The Book of the Ones ",
    "iti24:0.3": "Chapter Three ",
    "iti24:0.4": "A Heap of Bones ",
    "iti24:1.1": "This was said by the Buddha, the Perfected One: that is what I heard. ",
    "iti24:2.1": "“Mendicants, one person roaming and transmigrating for an eon would amass a heap of bones the size of this Mount Vepulla, if they were gathered together and not lost.” ",
    "iti24:2.2": "The Buddha spoke this matter. ",
    "iti24:2.3": "On this it is said: ",
    "iti24:3.1": "“If the bones of a single individual ",
    "iti24:3.2": "for a single eon were gathered up, ",
    "iti24:3.3": "they’d make a pile the size of a mountain: ",
    "iti24:3.4": "so said the great seer. ",
    "iti24:4.1": "And this is declared to be ",
    "iti24:4.2": "as huge as Mount Vepulla, ",
    "iti24:4.3": "higher than the Vulture’s Peak ",
    "iti24:4.4": "near the Mountainfold of the Magadhans. ",
    "iti24:5.1": "But then, with right understanding, ",
    "iti24:5.2": "one sees the noble truths—",
    "iti24:5.3": "suffering, suffering’s origin, ",
    "iti24:5.4": "suffering’s transcendence, ",
    "iti24:5.5": "and the noble eightfold path ",
    "iti24:5.6": "that leads to the stilling of suffering. ",
    "iti24:6.1": "After roaming on seven times at most, ",
    "iti24:6.2": "that individual ",
    "iti24:6.3": "makes an end of suffering, ",
    "iti24:6.4": "with the ending of all fetters.” ",
    "iti24:7.1": "This too is a matter that was spoken by the Blessed One: that is what I heard. "
  },
